<h2>Sorry, there are no Orientation sessions available at this time.</h2> 

In order to attend an Orientation, you <b>must register in advance</b>. (Walk-ins won't be admitted). All of the Sessions that have been opened for registration are full and no more seats are available.

Orientations are held Mondays at 7:30pm, Wednesdays at 10am and Sundays at 4pm. Sessions are made available for online registration exactly two weeks before the session start time (so, for instance, a 4:00 p.m. Orientation on the 20th of the month would become available for registration at 4:00 p.m. on the 6th of that same month). We encourage you to come back and try to sign up as new Sessions are made available online.

In the meantime, we recommend that you <a href="/login">Create an Account</a> if you have not done so already. Creating an account ahead of time will help your chances of getting a seat at an Orientation Session when you return to the site at a later date. Please also feel free to explore our website to learn more about the Coop and Coop Membership.

We appreciate your interest in the Park Slope Food Coop and hope to be seeing you soon.


